<h2>
About Brendan Seaton
</h2>

<p>
Brendan Seaton is an artist, writer and educator living in Toronto, Canada.  He works in two domains: Fine Art Photography and eHealth Risk Management.  While seemingly disparate, each is pursued with passion.  He splits his time equally between these two activities.
</p>

<p>
A photographer since he was 8 years of age, Brendan’s images capture the essence of the human spirit in the world.  His images are complemented by his writings, which explore one man’s journey into life.
</p>

<p>
For the past 25 years Brendan has been a leader in the field of health informatics.  For the past 15 years he has specialized in the privacy and security of health information.  Recently Brendan decided to widen the circle of his inquiry to include all aspects risk management in the eHealth domain including issues of privacy, security safety, business and project risk.
</p>

